column5: ALRIGHT CANADA!!!!  YYYEEEEEEEEAAAHHH!!  Go Canada GO.  HD

HOLY BUCKETS DUDE!!! haha. what a form of expressing excitement... HOLY BUCKETS!  canada's goin for gold! cheer for your country you communists! hahaha.......  like i already said in my other post "just razzin' "  GO CANADA GO!!
yea! keeping it close for the fans, GO CANADA
I don't know what's worse...destroying bad teams 15 - 0 or nearly losing to one (again). Yipes
Good thing Crosby had that second chance..  WHAT A GAME!!
oh ya! a couple of real cool saves in that shoot out too! (i dont watch hockey much so i thought they were cool haha)
God job guys..Put this one behind you. Joe
At least they kept it interesting.
Gota give it to Jonas Hiller .. he played a good game.
good thing Brodeur was between the pipes, cause we sure needed him tonight.
It's great that they won, but that cost us a valuable point! (We got 2 pts instead of 3) We won't get the #1 seed now, which will be a big loss.
Just got up and see the Russians went down to Slovakia in a shootout, getting very interesting..
WOW, I didn't know that! That's a huge bonus!
Yes, Canada beats the US and Russia takes the Czechs, we have #1 seed.  Unless I'm missing something
who cares about #1 seed. top 4 teams get a bye to the quarter finals
Tomorrow afternoon will be interesting. Joe
